sd=Position Management	The Service Domain tracks the bank's consolidated financial positions for major customers and complex market conditions	A major corporate or institutional customer's consolidated position is refenced when the corporate customer sufferes a major incident	Maintain on-line and near-time cross account complex positions. Includes consolidated currency, instrument, sector and counterparty views as appropriate
sdpath=position-management
crpath=financial-position-state
crr=Financial Position State Instance
mcr=Financial Position State
bqs=TrialTransaction TransactionApplication
CONFIG
FinancialPositionState	initiate	Initialize a monitored financial position		initiateFinancialPositionState		#desc
FinancialPositionState	update	Update the settings and notification arrangements for a position		updateFinancialPositionState		#desc
FinancialPositionState	control	Change the status/handling of a monitored position		controlFinancialPositionState		#desc
FinancialPositionState	retrieve	Get details and the current value of a monitored position		retrieveFinancialPositionState		#desc
TrialTransaction	initiate	Initiate the evaluation impact of a trial transaction	initiateFinancialPositionStateTrialTransaction	initiateFinancialPositionStateTrialTransaction		Details of a new Trial Transaction instance
TrialTransaction	update	Update details of a trial transaction	updateFinancialPositionStateTrialTransaction	updateFinancialPositionStateTrialTransaction		Update to any amendable fields of the Trial Transaction instance
TrialTransaction	retrieve	Retrieve details about a trial transaction and its position impact	retrieveFinancialPositionStateTrialTransaction	retrieveFinancialPositionStateTrialTransaction		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Trial Transaction instance related report
TransactionApplication	initiate	Initiate the registering of a transaction against the position	initiateFinancialPositionStateTransactionApplication	initiateFinancialPositionStateTransactionApplication		Details of a new Transaction Application instance
TransactionApplication	update	Update details of a registered transaction	updateFinancialPositionStateTransactionApplication	updateFinancialPositionStateTransactionApplication		Update to any amendable fields of the Transaction Application instance
TransactionApplication	retrieve	Retrieve details about a registered transaction and its position impact	retrieveFinancialPositionStateTransactionApplication	retrieveFinancialPositionStateTransactionApplication		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Transaction Application instance related report
